				<p style="color: black; font-weight: 700;">Music<br><span style="color: #989898;">iPhone SE</span></p>
				
			</div>
			<div class="three columns">
				<p style="color: black; font-weight: 700;">Podcasts<br><span style="color: #989898;">iPhone 8</span></p>
			</div>
			<div class="three columns">
				<p style="color: black; font-weight: 700;">Comedy<br><span style="color: #989898;">iPhone X</span></p>
